{"tid":293128,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大灣區研討會 北大出身學者 倡澳門與內地分享賭收","createTime":"2017-06-22T02:08:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-22T02:48:53.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3f77bb34e01310da9317f6d9dd16c5f69124f4ba","tid":293128,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T02:08:45.000Z","msg":"&lt;澳門與大陸分享賭收？&gt;<br />\n嘩！？呢個時候真是要直線抽擊！<br />\n大灣區美其名咩發展經濟，但係原來要係澳門人的庫房到搶錢！<br />\n私樓俾人炒買，公屋俾新澳門人搶。<br />\n女多男少又被大陸人搶走筍盤！<br />\n生活空間受到壓迫，出街無野玩。<br />\n<br />\n你老尾呢件來自北大係澳門理工的教授而家仲要謀澳門人的賭收！提倡共享？鬼同你血濃於水共患難。<br />\n真是佛都有火！<br />\n<br />\n#分享賭收就唔夠錢現金分享喇<br />\n#無現金分享方丈擔心生番會燒咗政總<br />\n#澳門人終於勇武起來<br />\n#講吓笑啫都係載返個頭盔先<br />\n<br />\n「理工學院博彩教學暨研究中心教授王長斌提到，內地或不想太多人來澳門賭博，導致內地人來澳不易，提議若本澳與內地分享博彩的收入，可能「有得傾」，讓內地開放更多旅客來澳旅遊。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.exmoo.com/article/35120.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.exmoo.com%2Farticle%2F35120.html&d=MMCia7h7ZnaEcZ%2FHRxIRewEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=28e27f2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.exmoo.com/article/35120.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/abbotmacau/photos/a.288535868156292.1073741828.254213211588558/487047388305138/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fabbotmacau%2Fphotos%2Fa.288535868156292.1073741828.254213211588558%2F487047388305138%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=MMCia7h7ZnaEcZ%2FHRxIRewEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=ce74a59f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/abbotmacau/photos/a.288535868156292.1073741828.254213211588558/487047388305138/?type=3</a>"},{"pid":"2892cec197cb20ebe1d23989588255109639a2b9","tid":293128,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T02:13:36.000Z","msg":"黎料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c35126b44d733c403fe4a6a0ae52f9ada2d532e5","tid":293128,"uid":16790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T02:47:23.000Z","msg":"死開